{"tid":1219810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【極醜惡】黑警已經進化到拎委任證坐霸王車","createTime":"2019-06-14T01:18:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T14:57:25.000Z","uid":35519,"like":3020,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":157,"replies":[{"pid":"e7826520f16b87aad1da1d6c801cb9eb9b292b95","tid":1219810,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:18:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/filmnbus/photos/a.1486693721374534/2382598061784091/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffilmnbus%2Fphotos%2Fa.1486693721374534%2F2382598061784091%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=10919c22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/filmnbus/photos/a.1486693721374534/2382598061784091/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aZCZD6v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaZCZD6v.jpg&h=0a10ede5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>其實年中都有啲警務人員<br />\n上車嘅時候哂張警員委任證比我哋車長睇<br />\n以便可以免費乘車</ins><br />\n為免卻不必要嘅麻煩<br />\n而好多師兄師姐們包括我睇到呢張證<br />\n都會隻眼開隻眼閉咁<br />\n默許佢哋咁樣搭順風車<br />\n感覺就好似潛規則一樣</strong><br />\n<br />\n尋晚新聞一幕幕令人心痛嘅畫面<br />\n一直喺腦內揮之不去<br />\n有鑑於昨日警方嘅野蠻暴戾行為<br />\n從今日起<br />\n我不會再接受所有非巴士公司發出嘅證件<br />\n亦即警員委任證不能用作乘車之用<br />\n請有關人士登車時支付該程車資<br />\n我亦希望同業可以一同嚴格執行<br />\n特此告之<br />\n<br />\n+ + + + +<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩各位巴絲﹐如果遇到巴士司機制止黑警坐霸王車時<br />\n即刻拎手機出黎﹐錄低佢地個狗樣<br />\n叫佢地展示個委任證﹐記實埋佢地個狗名同狗號<br />\n然後放上連登/FB<br />\n順便send去各大傳媒<br />\n向公務員事務局&amp; ICAC舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d42317d6403b9f63ac8e3e238aa73bbb8d3e50","tid":1219810,"uid":120555,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:20:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6821625061d332130e8769dfe34439c20edf900","tid":1219810,"uid":46656,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"支持！"},{"pid":"38b946797cc529066cb1d13f7752c454ee6ab8e6","tid":1219810,"uid":57151,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fdfc2e9f1052f4e434d76aae6f6a97d148c2384","tid":1219810,"uid":14918,"like":393,"dislike":0,"score":393,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:23:18.000Z","msg":"黑警唔係好高人工咩"},{"pid":"f982ef8a86c159e80f7050d90a110593ff901c0c","tid":1219810,"uid":85774,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:23:46.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"9734d49572150594aee094ff0783060cbf168e0c","tid":1219810,"uid":229289,"like":367,"dislike":1,"score":366,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:24:30.000Z","msg":"仲衰過班廢老 兩蚊都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bef1f9c53074f3d5ec46c6a3f3b45ef13d79cb3e","tid":1219810,"uid":193436,"like":567,"dislike":0,"score":567,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:27:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09aa84bbf694c925d721193b9c5303dde7f49baf","tid":1219810,"uid":166622,"like":77,"dislike":2,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:29:28.000Z","msg":"少少錢都唔比 你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衰過狗"},{"pid":"1da9c07c945c3578dc2b751df338c71f209552ec","tid":1219810,"uid":87511,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:29:40.000Z","msg":"記得出聲就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一定會幫你手啊巴士佬"},{"pid":"bdb38ddd53688839356dab1817eb1d361777c6d1","tid":1219810,"uid":82547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c231ed92b4b56ed