/>\n有機會食2家茶禮，唔比錢但又claim 車費<br />\n我地應該去邊度投訴"},{"pid":"924812c365d2e1989523be0fe75f96f7876a0232","tid":1219810,"uid":54616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:43:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1945f433bdbe5e4c82112d0cd8045076c9f4a0e","tid":1219810,"uid":142798,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:43:56.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"64e834e2c3163fbdbabe41055d936f3e31243133","tid":1219810,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:44:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">法西斯</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b923f114d2ba9543e4e9c69c815f77e7a5abf831","tid":1219810,"uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從今日起<br />\n我不會再接受所有非巴士公司發出嘅證件<br />\n亦即警員委任證不能用作乘車之用<br />\n請有關人士登車時支付該程車資<br />\n我亦希望同業可以一同嚴格執行<br />\n特此告之</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n支持巴士司機！"},{"pid":"d0978ad5f1f813f1fc9b893bd6e3b9faca23180a","tid":1219810,"uid":45788,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b57e69659c6c9007572757da3b486a4427caef06","tid":1219810,"uid":158700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:45:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b5521a68026cfc8ee5bb4590d92b01c5a5c206d2","tid":1219810,"uid":224860,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:45:22.000Z","msg":"基本上大部分前線警察都係欺善怕惡<br />\n記住自己應有嘅權利<br />\n睇下呢條影片就知 <br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/gkv36k14\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2Fgkv36k14&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=911bdb2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/gkv36k14</a><br />\n專恰後生仔 千祈唔好俾佢兇到 <br />\n根本無野好驚 要冷靜<br />\n<br />\n(1)警察有權查身分證<br />\n向15歲或以上之香港居民查閱身分證<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果查你身分證或護照,你照俾佢,無問題 但你有權保持緘默,即係只要向警方提供個人姓名及住址(ONLY區) ,其他都可以唔答<br />\n<br />\n(2)警察搜身<br />\n根據《警隊條例》（第232章）第54(2)條，警察頂要有合理懷疑必須根據事實情況而作出客觀判斷先可以搜物<br />\n警務人員不可以向異性進行搜身。 如要向一位女性搜身，而當時沒有女警在場，該女子便應被帶到最就近的警署，由女警為她進行搜身。<br />\n<br />\n(3)你有權用電話影住警察,用電話影呀SIR係要保障自己, 香港從沒有市民因拍下警察照片而被定罪的情況，以一般拍攝而言，理論上亦不涉襲警，故市民無需擔心。"},{"pid":"c63232a8038bb5a45711a79711dce26f57cf67a7","tid":1219810,"uid":194135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:45:46.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36092e257a4c405749da6bb580b186841911eaf4","tid":1219810,"uid":134854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:46:04.000Z","msg":"wish"},{"pid":"27c2f39640d05189edff18f92a9299e7d1a00ab2","tid":1219810,"uid":29080,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:46:30.000Z","msg":"委任證可免費乘車？可免費叫雞？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9343c1cc6d90e137a163e379fa8873f6d5ce0d43","tid":1219810,"uid":123591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:46:54.000Z","msg":"正宗乞衣"},{"pid":"3a74b28327e4663c6dc785f21e0a2c2f5dfea18b","tid":1219810,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26fa4ffbaf4e07f7a57be20eb2d81215413aa113","tid":1219810,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:48:08.000Z","msg":"推 平時已經咁醜惡"},{"pid":"1e9c38b2daedf86fd7b54ea9438b91fea60256a6","tid":1219810,"uid":161263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01:48:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e911db7a911a0bc3650aabb7d4fe2c1722e628f","tid":1219810,"uid":14328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T01