2","tid":1219810,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:07:55.000Z","msg":"支持 推 <br />\n屌你老母 依家咩年代 仲好似收規咁 成班都係生蕃黎"},{"pid":"0b81e35d1a5b71537b9d576cb2a8e27108337223","tid":1219810,"uid":5809,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"原來唔係警犬係乞兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁多位香港人,大家認為星期日上街係為左咩!?<br />\n<br />\n為左抗惡法?無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗迫林鄭下台?無錯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但最重要既係保護香港人!!!!!!!!!!</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時最少已經有11個香港人為咗我地被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中包括為咗我地而食棍!!!中椒!!!同埋中槍既香港人!!!!!!<br />\n星期日上街我地一定要為佢地發聲!!!唔可以忘記佢地!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家集中目標:<br />\n1.撤回送中惡法<br />\n2.林鄭及相關官員必須問責下台<br />\n3.釋放所有被捕人士及保證不會檢控任何示威者<br />\n4.起訴涉嫌謀殺之警員及其上司<br />\n5.成立具效力之警方濫用暴力調查組織<br />\n6.釋放所有在囚政治人士,包括黃之鋒及梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人,記得一個都不能少!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n唔可以放棄任何一個自己人!!!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"76c1623d938ef239854ef8114c337bdbf1b13ab1","tid":1219810,"uid":155270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:08:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母仆街死黑警個個月攞今撚高人工車錢都唔比，祝你地有錢冇命享"},{"pid":"4c0026eadeda68e1d85a71c8cc537f741a30a7c2","tid":1219810,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"有強權無公理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地唔可以再畀佢地沉淪落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/big